@startuml C4_Context_Diagram
!define RECTANGLE class
skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam rectangleBorderColor #555
skinparam arrowColor #444
skinparam actorBorderColor #333

title ScribeHealth AI — C4 Context Diagram

actor "Doctor\n(Healthcare Provider)" as Doctor #LightSteelBlue
actor "Administrator\n(Clinic Admin)" as Admin #LightSalmon
actor "Patient\n(Recipient)" as Patient #PaleGreen

rectangle "ScribeHealth AI\n[Software System]\n\nAI-powered medical scribe that records\nconsultations, transcribes audio, extracts\nmedical entities, generates SOAP notes,\nand manages review-approval workflows." as System #LightYellow

cloud "Sarvam AI\n[External System]\nsaarika:v2.5 Speech-to-Text\n(Hindi/English STT)" as Sarvam #FFFACD
cloud "Anthropic Claude\n[External System]\nHaiku (entity extraction)\nSonnet (SOAP generation)" as Claude #FFF3E0
cloud "Supabase\n[External System]\nPostgreSQL + Storage\n+ Realtime" as Supabase #E8F5E9
cloud "Notification Channels\n[External System]\nEmail · WhatsApp · SMS" as Notify #F3E5F5

Doctor --> System : "Records consultations,\nreviews & approves AI notes,\nmanages patients [HTTPS]"
Admin --> System : "Manages user accounts,\nviews audit logs [HTTPS]"
System --> Patient : "Shares approved notes\n& prescriptions [Email/SMS/WA]"

System --> Sarvam : "Sends audio buffer,\nreceives transcript [HTTPS REST]"
System --> Claude : "Sends transcript,\nreceives entities + SOAP note [HTTPS REST]"
System --> Supabase : "Persists patients, sessions,\nnotes, audit logs [TLS]"
System --> Notify : "Delivers note-ready,\napproved, and sharing alerts"

note right of System
  FR-01 to FR-12 fully implemented
  NFR-01: TLS + JWT (8-hr expiry)
  NFR-02: Async transcription pipeline
  NFR-03: Factory + Template Method patterns
  NFR-04: Immutable audit log
  NFR-05: Retry (3× with backoff)
end note

@enduml
